  "steps": [
    "Dock the potatoes with a toothpick.",
    "Boil some water in a deep non-stick pan, add ½ teaspoon salt, potatoes and cook till half done. Drain and pat dry.",
    "Take yogurt in a bowl, add turmeric powder, dried fenugreek leaves powder, dried mango powder, roasted gram flour, garam masala powder, red chilli powder, ½ teaspoon salt, Kashmiri red chilli paste, ginger-garlic paste and mustard oil and mix well.",
    "Add boiled potatoes and mix well. Set aside to marinate for 30-40 minutes.",
    "Preheat the air fryer to 190° C for 2 minutes. Line air fryer basket with aluminium foil and arrange the potatoes in single layer. Fir the basket to the air fryer and air fry for 10 minutes.",
    "Spray some oil and air fry for 5 minutes more.",
    "Bring the basket out of the air fryer, arrange the potatoes in a bowl and serve hot with green chutney, lemon rings and lemon wedges."
